#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:126
msgid "In this subsection you should list which third party payment processors you’re using to take payments on your store since these may handle customer data. We’ve included PayPal as an example, but you should remove this if you’re not using PayPal."
msgstr "Azpiatal honetan, zure dendan ordainketak onartzeko kanpoko zein beste ordainketa-prozesadore erabiltzen ari zaren adierazi beharko zenuke, baliteke bezeroen datuak erabiltzea. PayPal sartu dugu adibide gisa, baina ezabatu egin beharko zenuke PayPal erabiltzen ez baduzu."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:121
msgid "In this section you should list who you’re sharing data with, and for what purpose. This could include, but may not be limited to, analytics, marketing, payment gateways, shipping providers, and third party embeds."
msgstr "Atal honetan norekin ari zaren datuak partekatzen eta zein helbururekin adierazi beharko zenuke. Horrek barne har litzake, baina ez dago soilik horretara mugatuta, analisiak, marketina, ordainketa-pasabideak, bidalketa-hornitzaileak eta hirugarrenen txertaketak."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:123
msgid "We share information with third parties who help us provide our orders and store services to you; for example --"
msgstr "Beste batzuekin informazioa partekatzen dugu, gure eskaerak eskaintzen eta zuretzat zerbitzuak kudeatzen laguntzen digutelako; adibidez --"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:110
msgid "We generally store information about you for as long as we need the information for the purposes for which we collect and use it, and we are not legally required to continue to keep it. For example, we will store order information for XXX years for tax and accounting purposes. This includes your name, email address and billing and shipping addresses."
msgstr "Normalean, informazioa biltzen eta erabiltzen dugun helburuetarako behar dugun denboran gordetzen dugu zuri buruzko informazioa, eta ez gaude legez informazio hori gordetzen jarraitzera behartuta. Adibidez, XXX urtetan zehar eskaerei buruzko informazioa gordeko dugu, zergen eta kontabilitatearen helburuetarako. Hor sartzen dira zure izena, posta elektronikoko helbidea eta fakturazio- eta bidalketa-helbideak."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:111
msgid "We will also store comments or reviews, if you choose to leave them."
msgstr "Iruzkinak edo balorazioak ere gordetzen ditugu, uztea aukeratzen baduzu."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:112
msgid "Who on our team has access"
msgstr "Gure taldeko nork du sarbidea?"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:113
msgid "Members of our team have access to the information you provide us. For example, both Administrators and Shop Managers can access:"
msgstr "Gure taldeko kideek eskura dute eskaintzen diguzun informazioa. Adibidez, dendako administratzaileak eta kudeatzaileak sar daitezke:"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:115
msgid "Order information like what was purchased, when it was purchased and where it should be sent, and"
msgstr "Eskaerei buruzko informazioa, hala nola zer erosi zen, noiz erosi zen eta nora bidali beharko litzatekeen, eta"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:116
msgid "Customer information like your name, email address, and billing and shipping information."
msgstr "Bezeroaren informazioa, hala nola zure izena, helbide elektronikoa, eta fakturazio- eta bidalketa-informazioa."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:118
msgid "Our team members have access to this information to help fulfill orders, process refunds and support you."
msgstr "Gure taldeko kideek informazio hori eskura dezakete eskaerak osatzen, itzulketak prozesatzen eta zuri euskarria ematen laguntzeko."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:119
msgid "What we share with others"
msgstr "Besteekin partekatzen duguna"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:99
msgid "When you purchase from us, we’ll ask you to provide information including your name, billing address, shipping address, email address, phone number, credit card/payment details and optional account information like username and password. We’ll use this information for purposes, such as, to:"
msgstr "Zerbait erosten diguzunean, zure izena, fakturazio-helbidea, bidalketa-helbidea, helbide elektronikoa, telefono-zenbakia, kreditu-/ordainketa-txartelaren xehetasunak eta aukerako informazio gehigarria (erabiltzaile-izena eta pasahitza, esaterako) emateko eskatzen dizugu. Informazio hori helburu hauetarako erabiliko dugu:"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:101
msgid "Send you information about your account and order"
msgstr "Zure kontuari eta eskaerari buruzko informazioa bidaltzea"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:102
msgid "Respond to your requests, including refunds and complaints"
msgstr "Zure eskaerei erantzutea, itzulketak eta erreklamazioak barne"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:103
msgid "Process payments and prevent fraud"
msgstr "Ordainketak prozesatzea eta iruzurra saihestea"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:104
msgid "Set up your account for our store"
msgstr "Konfiguratu zure kontua gure dendarako"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:105
msgid "Comply with any legal obligations we have, such as calculating taxes"
msgstr "Legezko edozein betebehar betetzea, hala nola zergen kalkuluak"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:106
msgid "Improve our store offerings"
msgstr "Gure dendako eskaintzak hobetzea"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:107
msgid "Send you marketing messages, if you choose to receive them"
msgstr "Sustapen-mezuak bidaltzea, jasotzea aukeratzen baduzu"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:109
msgid "If you create an account, we will store your name, address, email and phone number, which will be used to populate the checkout for future orders."
msgstr "Kontu bat sortzen baduzu, zure izena, helbidea, posta elektronikoa eta telefono-zenbakia gordeko ditugu, eta hori ordainketa-prozesurako eta etorkizuneko eskaeretarako erabiliko dugu."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:95
msgid "We’ll also use cookies to keep track of cart contents while you’re browsing our site."
msgstr "Halaber, cookieak erabiltzen ditugu saskiaren edukien jarraipena egiteko gure gunean nabigatzen duzun bitartean."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:97
msgid "Note: you may want to further detail your cookie policy, and link to that section from here."
msgstr "Oharra: baliteke zure cookie-politika zehaztu nahi izatea, eta hemendik atal honetara lotzea."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:93
msgid "Shipping address: we’ll ask you to enter this so we can, for instance, estimate shipping before you place an order, and send you the order!"
msgstr "Bidalketa helbidea: hau sartzeko eskatuko dizugu, horrela eskaria egin aurretik bidalketaren estimazioa egin ahal izango dugu eta eskaria bidali!"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:92
msgid "Location, IP address and browser type: we’ll use this for purposes like estimating taxes and shipping"
msgstr "Kokapena, IP helbidea eta nabigatzaile mota: hori erabiliko dugu zergak eta bidalketa-kostuak kalkulatzeko."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:91
msgid "Products you’ve viewed: we’ll use this to, for example, show you products you’ve recently viewed"
msgstr "Ikusi dituzun produktuak: Adibidez, duela gutxi ikusi dituzun produktuak erakusteko erabiliko ditugu"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:87
msgid "We collect information about you during the checkout process on our store."
msgstr "Zure informazioa biltzen dugu ordainketa prozesuan zehar gure dendan."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:88
msgid "What we collect and store"
msgstr "Bildu eta biltegiratzen duguna"

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:89
msgid "While you visit our site, we’ll track:"
msgstr "Gure gunea bisitatzen duzun bitartean, honako hauen jarraipena egingo dugu:"

